### What problem does this feature solve?

在使用Radio.Button的分组时，经常会用到适合父级宽度的单选组，效果如下：
![184441](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fdbd0c99-5c1e-4d32-904d-42c8cf68bb32)

### What does the proposed API look like?

```jsx
<Radio.Group
  options={[
    {
      label: '全部',
      value: 'all',
    },
    {
      label: '未读',
      value: 'unread',
    },
    {
      label: '已读',
      value: 'read',
    },
  ]}
  optionType="button"
  buttonStyle="solid"
  block // <-
/>
```

